Audit the nullability in this schema. I'm deliberately allowing null on some fields because this is a federated subgraph and some fields are resolved by other services:

type Query {
  product(id: ID!): Product
  searchProducts(query: String!): [Product!]!
}

type Product {
  id: ID!
  name: String!
  price: Float!
  externalRating: Float
  supplierInfo: SupplierInfo
  tags: [String!]!
}

type SupplierInfo {
  supplierId: ID!
  name: String
  contactEmail: String
}
